  resvar;
  [resvar];
  resvar2-resvar19@0;
  [resvar2-resvar19@0];

  [beta_y](a);
  [beta_s](b);

  mu day_ar resvar_1 resvar resvar_2 night_ar-resvar_s s WITH
     mu day_ar resvar_1 resvar resvar_2 night_ar-resvar_s s;

  mu night_ar day_ar resvar_1 resvar resvar_2 ON N;
  beta_y delta_y beta_s ar_s s resvar_s ON N;
  mu night_ar day_ar resvar_1 resvar resvar_2 ON C;
  beta_y delta_y beta_s ar_s s resvar_s ON C;
  C;
